{"word":"G4383 - πρόσωπον - prósōpon - pros'-o-pon - Appearance","slug":"G4383","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πρόσωπον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>prósōpon"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>pros'-o-pon"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Appearance"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03C3;&#x03C9;&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x03BD; - proso&#x0304;pon</b> - <i>pros'-o-pon</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4314\">G4314</a> and <b>&#x03C9;&#x0313;&#x0301;&#x03C8;</b> <b>o&#x0304;ps</b> (the <i>visage</i>; from <a href=\"#/G3700\">G3700</a>); the <i>front</i> (as being <i>towards view</i>), that is, the <i>countenance</i>, <i>aspect</i>, <i>appearance</i>, <i>surface</i>; by implication <i>presence</i>, <i>person:</i> - (outward) appearance, X before, countenance, face, fashion, (men&rsquo;s) person, presence."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2146\">G2146</a>, <a href=\"#/G4380\">G4380</a>, <a href=\"#/G4381\">G4381</a>, <a href=\"#/G4382\">G4382</a>, <a href=\"#/G678\">G678</a>"}]}